biography: Alexander Hendorf is an independent AI strategy consultant with over 20 years of experience in digitalization and data-driven transformation. Through his commitment as a speaker and chair of various international conferences, he is a proven expert in the field of data intelligence. He has extensive experience in the practical application, introduction and communication of data and AI-driven strategies and decision-making processes. He is a Python Software Foundation Fellow, EuroPython Fellow, and co-founder of Pioneers Hub. He likes to work in small dedicated teams and loves to work with and contribute to the Python and PyData community.
